  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To determine the acquisition rate of ESBL producing E. coli or K. pneumoniae, post-
      intervention in the selected medical centres
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This is post-interventional study to follow the acquisition rate of ESBP producing E. coli or
      K. pneumoniae at the sites involved in a previous interventional study.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
